Package de.hsb.ms.syn.common.vo

Node classes used by the Desktop host to represent sound entities, which are also capable of arranging themselves along sound paths.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CenterNode
    Center node class.
    DraggableNode
    Base class for Nodes that can be dragged around with the mouse.
    FxNode
    FX Node An FX Node can't produce audio data itself, but rather it modifies the incoming signal from its inputs.
    GenNode
    Gen Node A Gen Node produces streams of audio based on mathematical functions.
    MicrophoneInputNode
    Microphone Input Node A Microphone Input Node obtains signals from the device's microphone in order to generate its buffer.
    Node
    Base class for a Node representation on the synthesizer's surface.
    NodesStage
    Special kind of Libgdx Stage object with the additional service of drawing connections for each Node
